How I miss the birds of my home world! My brother Ihipura once taught me to invoke their animas for aid. If you bring me a small bundle of feathers from the Siraluun that roam the island, I will ask Siraluun to help me make a special headdress for you. Even better, if you combine five of the smaller bundles into a larger one, I will make a lovely dress. Here, add the bundles to this special bag, it will keep them from getting rumpled.
